      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA code (Ansys) used under documented QMS; FDA internal code under SQA plan. Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 R2 used under a documented software quality management plan including version control, regression testing, and change control. FDA in-house code independently verified against analytical benchmarks. Required level 2 achieved."
