      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (ASTM F1717 compression-bending) is the same scenario as the COU; no extrapolation beyond validated domain required.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: ASTM F1717 static compression-bending of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. No extrapolation to untested geometries or loading modes is required for the intended submission use. Required level 3 achieved."
